title._content: Page 39 of Accounting Administration from Financial Ledger from  World's Columbian Exposition 1893

description._content:
"Electric Lights and Appliances." heading of Page 39 of the World's Columbian Exposition Financial Ledger, which continues the accounting from page 38  May 31, 1893 through August 31, 1894

Digital Identifier: GN90799d_WCEledger_039
Original material: Digital capture from original ledger.
Original date of object: 1892-1894
Digital file created 2003

Select pages from the Financial Ledger on display during The Field Museum's exhibition;Opening the Vaults: Wonders of the 1893 World's Fair; October 25, 2013 - September 7, 2013.
